properties.name: expanded
properties.description: Specifies whether or not the tree view item is displayed expanded.

properties.name: hasItems
properties.description: Specifies whether or not the tree view item has children.

properties.name: icon
properties.description: Specifies the tree view item's icon.

properties.name: id
properties.description: Holds the unique key of an item.

properties.name: parentId
properties.description: Holds the key of the parent item.

properties.name: selected
properties.description: Specifies whether the TreeView item should be displayed as selected.
